					<tr valign="top">
						<td width="15">1)</td>
						<td>Beef brisket is rinsed with cold water and boiled as a whole with radish until it is tender</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>2)</td>
						<td>Radish is drained and sliced, and beef is thick-sliced and these are seasoned with green onions, garlic, and soy sauce, put into the soup to boil.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>3)</td>
						<td>Brackens and roots of Chinese bellflower are trimmed and stir-fried with seasonings.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>4)</td>
						<td>Beansprouts are boiled and seasoned.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>5)</td>
						<td>Beef round is minced, seasoned, flattened, grilled and cut in squares.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>6)</td>
						<td>Cooked rice is put in the earthenware and hot soup is poured on it, and then beef squares and seasoned vegetables are arranged on top of it.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr><td colspan="2"><img src="/common/images/trans.gif" width="1" height="7" border="0"></td></tr>
					<tr valign="top">
						<td>7)</td>
						<td>When eating, green onions, sesame powder, or red pepper powder is added according to the preferences.</td>
					</tr>
